---
title: Cheat's Creamy Double Bacon & Veggie Filo Pie  with Parmesan & Rocket
description: Crispy and creamy! Golden filo pastry blankets a rich filling of smokey bacon and wholesome, pre-prepped vegetables (like potato, carrot and pumpkin) in a velvety sauce. Served with a peppery rocket salad for a fresh, satisfying crunch. It's comfort food made simple.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y25_R1039_W50_AU_R49225-2_Main_high-0a81b6ac.jpg
